# Moyu — Anti-Over-Engineering

Only change what was asked. Simplest solution first. When unsure, ask.

Do not: modify unrequested code, add abstractions without being asked, add comments/docs/tests without being asked, import unnecessary dependencies, rewrite entire files for small changes, add error handling for impossible scenarios.

Before delivery: verify you only changed requested code, check for simpler approaches, confirm no unrequested files were touched.
